---
title: Chargrilled Greek-Style Chicken with Honey Haloumi, Garlic Couscous & Mint Yoghurt
description: Make dinner a fast, easy, Greek-style affair with herby chargrilled chicken. Paired with squeaky haloumi, garlicky couscous and flatbreads, it's a winning barbeque meal. No barbie? No worries. Just follow our tips for cooking on the stove or in the oven!
